org.digijava.kernel.ampapi.endpoints.activity

Class ActivityErrors

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.digijava.kernel.ampapi.endpoints.activity.ActivityErrors

  • public class ActivityErrors
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines errors used by Activity API. Please define concrete errors, normally is an invalid request input.
    Anything that is out of control, should be re-thrown and it will be handled by API Exception Filter.
